        "action": "Review accessibility of driving tests for people with SEN",
        "additional_details": "I would like the theory test to be more accessible to have two tests one for hazard perception and then another one for the multiple-choice. With all the support in place.",
        "background": "I call on the Government to review the accessibility of the driving theory test, to make it more accessible for children with special educational needs (SEN). ",
